name: Fullmetal Alchemist: The Conqueror of Shamballa
description: Munich, 1923: Two years have passed since Ed was ripped away from his world. In his new reality, the growing Nazi Party threatens two worlds. With occult forces and Homunculi lurking in the shadows, alchemy and modern science are set to collide.
